# arch linux wiki install
## font location for all users: /usr/share/fonts
### set file permissions to at least 0444 (0555 for directories)
## font location for single user: ~/.local/share/fonts (~/.fonts is deprecated)
# for xserver to load fonts directly (not via font server) the font must be added
# to the files section of the xorg configuration file
# /etc/X11/xorg.conf or /etc/xorg.conf
# create skeleton with: Xorg :0 -configure

